casebody.data:
Alfredo PRIETO, petitioner,
v.
Harold W. CLARKE, Director, Virginia Department of Corrections, et al. No. 15-31. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 13, 2015.

Motion of Mark Eric Lawlor for leave to intervene denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit dismissed as moot.
